  "description": "A component that integrates with locally-hosted language models through Ollama. \nIt enables on-premise text generation, summarization, and question answering \nwithout relying on external APIs. Ideal for privacy-sensitive applications, the \ncomponent offers low-latency inference and supports various open-source models. It \nallows organizations to leverage LLM capabilities while maintaining full control \nover data and infrastructure.",
